name: Hybrid Hydrangea
description:
It’s Christmas time! Here is a beautiful and affordable gift you could make to yourself or someone you love. 

« Hydrangea » is one of the selected outcome that came from my exploration of neural networks capabilities to generate art. Most of my inputs, if not all, include my main obsessions : rose gold and cyanotypes. You will always find a touch of rose gold and cyanotype in my work, « Hybrid Hydrangea » is no exception.
